FBIS3-58442 "drweu009_p_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-009 Document Type:Daily Report 13 Jan 1994 GREECE Navy Spokesman Denies Violation of Albanian Waters NC1201190494 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1800 GMT 12 Jan 94 NC1201190494 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Language: Greek Article Type:BFN [Text] The Navy General Staff press spokesman denied a statement by the Albanian Defense Ministry that last Monday [10 January] Greek ships violated the Albanian territorial waters. According to the spokesman, the sole purpose of the torpedo boat and the patrol ship posted in that area is to avert the entry of illegal immigrants into our country. The Albanian Defense Ministry protested to the Greek authorities and noted that this was the 3d violation of the Albanian territorial waters by Greek ships in less than two months.
